videos.description: Mike Weber scores the first touchdown of the game with a 9-yard touchdown run to give Ohio State a 10-3 lead over Indiana.
videos.headline: Weber runs outside for 9-yard touchdown

videos.description: Facing 3rd and Long, Richard Lagow connects with Nick Westbrook to flip the field

videos.headline: Buckeyes increase lead with Samuel TD

videos.description: After a 91-yard kickoff return set Ohio State up with excellent field position, J.T. Barrett keeps it and runs in the touchdown from five yards out to give the Buckeyes a 24-10 lead over Indiana.
videos.headline: Ohio State goes back up two TDs with Barrett's run
